   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"nbformat\": 4, \"nbformat_minor\": 5,\n",
    " \"metadata\": {\"kernelspec\": {\"display_name\": \"Python 3\", \"language\": \"python\", \"name\": \"python3\"}, \"language_info\": {\"name\": \"python\", \"version\": \"3.11.0\"}},\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"# Semantic Router Project\\n\", \"\\n\", \"**NLP Project 99 of 100 · Advanced and Research-Style NLP**\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Project Overview\\n\", \"\\n\", \"This notebook builds a **semantic router** that classifies incoming user queries by intent and routes them to the appropriate specialized NLP pipeline (QA, summarization, translation, code generation, sentiment analysis). Routing is based on embedding similarity rather than keyword matching.\\n\", \"\\n\", \"**Models:** Sentence-Transformers (`all-MiniLM-L6-v2`) for intent embeddings, TF-IDF baseline\\n\", \"\\n\", \"**Metrics:** Routing accuracy, confidence distribution, fallback rate\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Learning Objectives\\n\", \"\\n\", \"1. Build an intent-based routing system using dense embeddings\\n\", \"2. Define routes with few-shot examples per intent category\\n\", \"3. Implement fallback handling for unrecognized queries\\n\", \"4. Compare embedding-based vs. keyword-based routing\\n\", \"5. Evaluate routing accuracy and analyze failure modes\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Problem Statement\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Given a natural language user query, the router must:\\n\", \"1. Compute semantic similarity against defined route examples\\n\", \"2. Select the best-matching route (or fallback if confidence is low)\\n\", \"3. Achieve high routing accuracy across diverse query phrasings\\n\", \"\\n\", \"This pattern is used in production chatbots, API gateways, and multi-agent systems.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Why This Project Matters\\n\", \"\\n\", \"- Modern NLP systems serve multiple capabilities — routing picks the right one\\n\", \"- Keyword routing breaks on paraphrased or ambiguous queries\\n\", \"- Semantic routing enables graceful fallback for out-of-scope queries\\n\", \"- This pattern is the backbone of multi-agent orchestration\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Dataset Overview\\n\", \"\\n\", \"| Property | Value |\\n\", \"|----------|-------|\\n\", \"| Routes | 5 intent categories |\\n\", \"| Examples per route | 5 few-shot examples each |\\n\", \"| Test queries | 20 labeled queries |\\n\", \"| Language | English |\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Dataset Source and License Notes\\n\", \"\\n\", \"All route examples and test queries are synthetically created within this notebook.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Environment Setup\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Required packages: `sentence-transformers`, `scikit-learn`, `pandas`, `numpy`, `matplotlib`\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Imports\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"import json, os, warnings\\n\", \"import numpy as np\\n\", \"import pandas as pd\\n\", \"import matplotlib\\n\", \"matplotlib.use(\\\"Agg\\\")\\n\", \"import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\n\", \"from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\n\", \"from sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity as sklearn_cosine\\n\", \"warnings.filterwarnings(\\\"ignore\\\")\\n\", \"SAVE_DIR = os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(\\\"__file__\\\"))\\n\", \"SEED = 42\\n\", \"np.random.seed(SEED)\\n\", \"print(\\\"Imports loaded.\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Configuration / Constants\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD = 0.40\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Routing threshold: {CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD}\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Dataset Download or Loading\\n\", \"\\n\", \"We define 5 intent routes with few-shot examples, plus a labeled test set.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"ROUTES = {\\n\", \"    \\\"qa\\\": [\\n\", \"        \\\"What is machine learning?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"How does Python work?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Explain neural networks to me\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"What are word embeddings?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"How does gradient descent optimize a model?\\\",\\n\", \"    ],\\n\", \"    \\\"summarize\\\": [\\n\", \"        \\\"Summarize this article for me\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Give me the key points of this document\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"TLDR of this long report\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Condense this text into a paragraph\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"What are the main takeaways from this paper?\\\",\\n\", \"    ],\\n\", \"    \\\"translate\\\": [\\n\", \"        \\\"Translate this to French\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Convert this text to Spanish\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Say this sentence in German\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"How do you say hello in Japanese?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Translate the following paragraph into Chinese\\\",\\n\", \"    ],\\n\", \"    \\\"code\\\": [\\n\", \"        \\\"Write Python code for sorting a list\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Generate a function that calculates Fibonacci numbers\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Create a script to scrape a website\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Code a binary search algorithm\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Implement a REST API endpoint in Python\\\",\\n\", \"    ],\\n\", \"    \\\"sentiment\\\": [\\n\", \"        \\\"What is the sentiment of this review?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Is this comment positive or negative?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Analyze the tone of this feedback\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"How does the customer feel about this product?\\\",\\n\", \"        \\\"Rate the emotional tone of this message\\\",\\n\", \"    ],\\n\", \"}\\n\", \"\\n\", \"TEST_QUERIES = [\\n\", \"    (\\\"What is deep learning?\\\", \\\"qa\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Explain how transformers work\\\", \\\"qa\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"What is transfer learning in NLP?\\\", \\\"qa\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Define reinforcement learning\\\", \\\"qa\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Summarize the document for me\\\", \\\"summarize\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Give me a brief overview of this report\\\", \\\"summarize\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"What are the highlights of this article?\\\", \\\"summarize\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Can you shorten this text?\\\", \\\"summarize\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Translate hello to Spanish\\\", \\\"translate\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Convert this to Japanese please\\\", \\\"translate\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"How would you say goodbye in French?\\\", \\\"translate\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Translate this paragraph to German\\\", \\\"translate\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Write a sorting function in Python\\\", \\\"code\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Build a calculator app\\\", \\\"code\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Code a web scraper using BeautifulSoup\\\", \\\"code\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Create a machine learning pipeline\\\", \\\"code\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Is this review positive?\\\", \\\"sentiment\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Analyze the mood of this tweet\\\", \\\"sentiment\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"What is the weather today?\\\", \\\"fallback\\\"),\\n\", \"    (\\\"Book me a flight to London\\\", \\\"fallback\\\"),\\n\", \"]\\n\", \"\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Routes: {list(ROUTES.keys())}\\\")\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Test queries: {len(TEST_QUERIES)}\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Data Validation Checks\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"assert len(ROUTES) >= 3\\n\", \"for route, examples in ROUTES.items():\\n\", \"    assert len(examples) >= 3\\n\", \"assert len(TEST_QUERIES) >= 10\\n\", \"print(\\\"Validation passed.\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Exploratory Data Analysis\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"route_sizes = {r: len(e) for r, e in ROUTES.items()}\\n\", \"print(\\\"Examples per route:\\\", route_sizes)\\n\", \"\\n\", \"test_labels = [t[1] for t in TEST_QUERIES]\\n\", \"fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 4))\\n\", \"pd.Series(test_labels).value_counts().plot.bar(ax=ax, color=\\\"steelblue\\\")\\n\", \"ax.set_ylabel(\\\"Count\\\")\\n\", \"ax.set_title(\\\"Test Query Distribution by Expected Route\\\")\\n\", \"ax.tick_params(axis='x', rotation=0)\\n\", \"plt.tight_layout()\\n\", \"plt.savefig(os.path.join(SAVE_DIR, \\\"eda_distributions.png\\\"), dpi=150, bbox_inches=\\\"tight\\\")\\n\", \"plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Target Analysis\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Each test query has an expected route label. The router must match queries to the correct intent. Fallback queries should not match any defined route.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Train / Validation / Test Split Strategy\\n\", \"\\n\", \"No train/test split — routing uses few-shot examples as prototypes and is evaluated on the labeled test set.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Preprocessing Strategy\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Encode route examples and queries using sentence-transformers. TF-IDF baseline computes lexical similarity.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer\\n\", \"\\n\", \"st_model = SentenceTransformer(\\\"all-MiniLM-L6-v2\\\")\\n\", \"\\n\", \"# Encode route examples\\n\", \"route_embeddings = {}\\n\", \"for route, examples in ROUTES.items():\\n\", \"    route_embeddings[route] = st_model.encode(examples, normalize_embeddings=True)\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Encoded {len(route_embeddings)} routes.\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Feature Engineering\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Dense embeddings capture semantic intent; TF-IDF captures keyword overlap.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Baseline Model\\n\", \"\\n\", \"**TF-IDF keyword matching** as baseline router.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"# Build TF-IDF baseline\\n\", \"all_examples = []\\n\", \"all_labels = []\\n\", \"for route, examples in ROUTES.items():\\n\", \"    all_examples.extend(examples)\\n\", \"    all_labels.extend([route] * len(examples))\\n\", \"\\n\", \"tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(stop_words=\\\"english\\\")\\n\", \"tfidf_matrix = tfidf.fit_transform(all_examples)\\n\", \"\\n\", \"def tfidf_route(query, threshold=0.15):\\n\", \"    q_vec = tfidf.transform([query])\\n\", \"    sims = sklearn_cosine(q_vec, tfidf_matrix).flatten()\\n\", \"    best_idx = int(sims.argmax())\\n\", \"    best_score = float(sims[best_idx])\\n\", \"    return (all_labels[best_idx], round(best_score, 3)) if best_score >= threshold else (\\\"fallback\\\", round(best_score, 3))\\n\", \"\\n\", \"print(\\\"=== TF-IDF Baseline Routing (sample) ===\\\")\\n\", \"for q, expected in TEST_QUERIES[:5]:\\n\", \"    route, score = tfidf_route(q)\\n\", \"    match = \\\"✓\\\" if route == expected else \\\"✗\\\"\\n\", \"    print(f\\\"  {match} [{route:10s}] (sim={score:.3f}) {q}\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## LazyPredict Benchmark\\n\", \"\\n\", \"> **Not applicable** for semantic routing tasks.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## FLAML AutoML Run\\n\", \"\\n\", \"> **Not applicable** for semantic routing tasks.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Dense Semantic Router\\n\", \"\\n\", \"Route queries by computing embedding similarity against each route's examples.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"def semantic_route(query, threshold=CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD):\\n\", \"    q_emb = st_model.encode([query], normalize_embeddings=True)\\n\", \"    best_route, best_score = \\\"fallback\\\", 0.0\\n\", \"    route_scores = {}\\n\", \"    for route, embs in route_embeddings.items():\\n\", \"        sims = (q_emb @ embs.T).flatten()\\n\", \"        max_sim = float(sims.max())\\n\", \"        route_scores[route] = round(max_sim, 3)\\n\", \"        if max_sim > best_score:\\n\", \"            best_score = max_sim\\n\", \"            best_route = route if max_sim >= threshold else \\\"fallback\\\"\\n\", \"    return best_route, round(best_score, 3), route_scores\\n\", \"\\n\", \"print(\\\"=== Semantic Router Results ===\\\")\\n\", \"routing_results = []\\n\", \"for q, expected in TEST_QUERIES:\\n\", \"    route, score, scores = semantic_route(q)\\n\", \"    match = \\\"✓\\\" if route == expected else \\\"✗\\\"\\n\", \"    routing_results.append({\\\"query\\\": q, \\\"expected\\\": expected, \\\"predicted\\\": route, \\\"score\\\": score, \\\"correct\\\": route == expected})\\n\", \"    print(f\\\"  {match} [{route:10s}] (sim={score:.3f}) {q}\\\")\\n\", \"\\n\", \"results_df = pd.DataFrame(routing_results)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Top 3 Model Selection\\n\", \"\\n\", \"We compare TF-IDF baseline vs. dense semantic routing.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Final Training and Evaluation of Top 3\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"# TF-IDF accuracy\\n\", \"tfidf_correct = sum(1 for q, expected in TEST_QUERIES if tfidf_route(q)[0] == expected)\\n\", \"tfidf_acc = tfidf_correct / len(TEST_QUERIES)\\n\", \"\\n\", \"# Semantic accuracy\\n\", \"sem_correct = results_df[\\\"correct\\\"].sum()\\n\", \"sem_acc = sem_correct / len(results_df)\\n\", \"\\n\", \"# Fallback analysis\\n\", \"fallback_queries = results_df[results_df[\\\"predicted\\\"] == \\\"fallback\\\"]\\n\", \"expected_fallback = results_df[results_df[\\\"expected\\\"] == \\\"fallback\\\"]\\n\", \"\\n\", \"print(\\\"=== Routing Accuracy ===\\\")\\n\", \"print(f\\\"  TF-IDF:    {tfidf_acc*100:.0f}% ({tfidf_correct}/{len(TEST_QUERIES)})\\\")\\n\", \"print(f\\\"  Semantic:  {sem_acc*100:.0f}% ({sem_correct}/{len(results_df)})\\\")\\n\", \"print(f\\\"\\\\nFallback: {len(fallback_queries)} queries routed to fallback\\\")\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Expected fallback: {len(expected_fallback)} queries\\\")\\n\", \"\\n\", \"# Per-route accuracy\\n\", \"print(\\\"\\\\n=== Per-Route Accuracy (Semantic) ===\\\")\\n\", \"for route in list(ROUTES.keys()) + [\\\"fallback\\\"]:\\n\", \"    subset = results_df[results_df[\\\"expected\\\"] == route]\\n\", \"    if len(subset) > 0:\\n\", \"        acc = subset[\\\"correct\\\"].mean()\\n\", \"        print(f\\\"  {route:10s}: {acc*100:.0f}% ({subset['correct'].sum()}/{len(subset)})\\\")\\n\", \"\\n\", \"# Visualization\\n\", \"fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 5))\\n\", \"axes[0].bar([\\\"TF-IDF\\\", \\\"Semantic\\\"], [tfidf_acc, sem_acc], color=[\\\"coral\\\", \\\"steelblue\\\"])\\n\", \"axes[0].set_ylabel(\\\"Accuracy\\\")\\n\", \"axes[0].set_title(\\\"Routing Accuracy\\\")\\n\", \"axes[0].set_ylim(0, 1)\\n\", \"\\n\", \"scores = results_df[\\\"score\\\"]\\n\", \"axes[1].hist(scores, bins=12, color=\\\"steelblue\\\", edgecolor=\\\"white\\\")\\n\", \"axes[1].axvline(CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD, color=\\\"red\\\", linestyle=\\\"--\\\", label=f\\\"Threshold={CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD}\\\")\\n\", \"axes[1].set_xlabel(\\\"Confidence Score\\\")\\n\", \"axes[1].set_ylabel(\\\"Count\\\")\\n\", \"axes[1].set_title(\\\"Routing Confidence Distribution\\\")\\n\", \"axes[1].legend()\\n\", \"plt.tight_layout()\\n\", \"plt.savefig(os.path.join(SAVE_DIR, \\\"routing_results.png\\\"), dpi=150, bbox_inches=\\\"tight\\\")\\n\", \"plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Error Analysis\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"errors = results_df[~results_df[\\\"correct\\\"]]\\n\", \"print(f\\\"Misrouted: {len(errors)}/{len(results_df)}\\\")\\n\", \"if len(errors) > 0:\\n\", \"    for _, row in errors.iterrows():\\n\", \"        print(f\\\"  '{row['query'][:50]}...' → predicted={row['predicted']}, expected={row['expected']} (score={row['score']})\\\")\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Interpretation and Business Insight\\n\", \"\\n\", \"1. **Semantic routing outperforms keyword matching** — handles paraphrases and diverse phrasing\\n\", \"2. **Few-shot examples per route** (5 each) are sufficient for good routing accuracy\\n\", \"3. **Fallback handling is critical** — out-of-scope queries must be caught gracefully\\n\", \"4. **Confidence threshold tuning** balances precision (correct routes) vs recall (avoiding unnecessary fallbacks)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Limitations\\n\", \"\\n\", \"1. Small number of routes and examples — production systems have 20-50+ intents\\n\", \"2. No dynamic route addition — routes are hardcoded\\n\", \"3. Single-intent routing — no multi-intent handling\\n\", \"4. No disambiguation — ambiguous queries go to highest-scoring route\\n\", \"5. Threshold is global — per-route thresholds could improve precision\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## How to Improve This Project\\n\", \"\\n\", \"1. Use the `semantic-router` library for production-grade routing\\n\", \"2. Add per-route confidence thresholds\\n\", \"3. Support multi-intent queries (return top-K routes)\\n\", \"4. Add route examples dynamically from user interaction logs\\n\", \"5. Fine-tune embedding model on domain-specific queries\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Production Considerations\\n\", \"\\n\", \"- Use `semantic-router` or similar library for scale\\n\", \"- Cache route embeddings — they don't change often\\n\", \"- Log routing decisions for monitoring and improvement\\n\", \"- Add per-route handlers with their own error handling\\n\", \"- Implement A/B testing for threshold tuning\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Common Mistakes\\n\", \"\\n\", \"| Mistake | Fix |\\n\", \"|---------|-----|\\n\", \"| Keyword-only routing | Use semantic embeddings |\\n\", \"| No fallback | Always handle out-of-scope queries |\\n\", \"| Fixed threshold | Tune per route or use calibration |\\n\", \"| Too few examples | Add 5-10 diverse examples per route |\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Mini Challenge / Exercises\\n\", \"\\n\", \"1. Add 3 more intent routes and evaluate accuracy\\n\", \"2. Implement multi-intent routing (return top-3 routes)\\n\", \"3. Build a threshold calibration system using a validation set\\n\", \"4. Add ambiguity detection (flag queries close to 2+ routes)\\n\", \"5. Compare routing with and without fine-tuned embeddings\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"markdown\", \"metadata\": {}, \"source\": [\"## Final Summary / Key Takeaways\\n\", \"\\n\", \"| # | Takeaway |\\n\", \"|---|----------|\\n\", \"| 1 | Semantic routing uses embedding similarity to match queries to intents |\\n\", \"| 2 | Few-shot examples per route are sufficient for decent routing |\\n\", \"| 3 | Fallback handling is critical for production robustness |\\n\", \"| 4 | Dense embeddings significantly outperform keyword matching |\\n\", \"| 5 | For production, use the semantic-router library or fine-tune on real query logs |\\n\", \"\\n\", \"---\\n\", \"*NLP Project 99 of 100 · Advanced and Research-Style NLP*\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\": \"code\", \"execution_count\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"outputs\": [], \"source\": [\"metrics = {\\n\", \"    \\\"project\\\": \\\"Semantic Router\\\",\\n\", \"    \\\"routes\\\": len(ROUTES),\\n\", \"    \\\"test_queries\\\": len(TEST_QUERIES),\\n\", \"    \\\"tfidf_accuracy_pct\\\": round(tfidf_acc * 100, 1),\\n\", \"    \\\"semantic_accuracy_pct\\\": round(sem_acc * 100, 1),\\n\", \"    \\\"confidence_threshold\\\": CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD,\\n\", \"}\\n\", \"with open(os.path.join(SAVE_DIR, \\\"metrics.json\\\"), \\\"w\\\") as f:\\n\", \"    json.dump(metrics, f, indent=2)\\n\", \"print(\\\"Saved: metrics.json\\\")\\n\", \"print(json.dumps(metrics, indent=2))\"]}\n",
    " ]\n",
    "}\n"
   ],
